  "detailed_description": "Hate Free Heroes is being updated to a 3D format with many enhancements. The new version will be available here:<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1645622590\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This older version will be discontinued on Steam and removed from Steam's store page but you will still have access to play the older version on Steam if you have purchased the game. <br><br>If you are interested in this game, be sure to wish list it for the 3D Enhanced version. We will announce a final sale for this older version and then remove it from Steam's store front. <br><br>Also wishlist the upcoming strategy mmo version as well.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1645622590\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Thank you everyone who has shown us support for our game over the years. We hope you enjoy our new enhanced version, we appreciate your continued support.",
  "about_the_game": "Hate Free Heroes is being updated to a 3D format with many enhancements. The new version will be available here:<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1645622590\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This older version will be discontinued on Steam and removed from Steam's store page but you will still have access to play the older version on Steam if you have purchased the game. <br><br>If you are interested in this game, be sure to wish list it for the 3D Enhanced version. We will announce a final sale for this older version and then remove it from Steam's store front. <br><br>Also wishlist the upcoming strategy mmo version as well.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1645622590\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/514540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1645622590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Thank you everyone who has shown us support for our game over the years. We hope you enjoy our new enhanced version, we appreciate your continued support."